metadata.name: Life Time Stone #1
metadata.description:
What is the meaning of the Stones?
uniqueness.

There is no one like you, even if there is
billions of people in the world, nobody, absolutely nobody
is just like you! As with natural stones, no
there is in nature one stone like another.

Each stone in the collection represents the uniqueness
of the one who owns it.

What is the meaning of Animals?
Movement.

Nothing beats practice and action! The animals follow their
instincts and live in constant motion, their processes
and routines are repeated day after day. those who most
act, become leaders, authorities and most importantly,
become examples!

What is the meaning of Trees?
Evolution.

Evolution of the environment, evolution of the individual,
evolution of knowledge and value in all of this!

What is the meaning of Waters?
Adaptation.

Escape the patterns, learn in other ways. life doesn't
can be stiff and boring, it needs to be fluid and light!
